Package com.microsoft.azure

This package contains the Azure rollup client.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Azure.Authenticated
    Provides authenticated access to a subset of Azure APIs that do not require a specific subscription.
    Azure.Configurable
    The interface allowing configurations to be made on the client.
    Page<E>
    Defines a page interface in Azure responses.
    TaskGroup<T,U extends TaskItem<T>>
    Represents a group of related tasks.
    TaskItem<U>
    Type representing a task in a task group TaskGroup.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Azure
    The entry point for accessing resource management APIs in Azure.
    AzureAsyncOperation
    The response body contains the status of the specified asynchronous operation, indicating whether it has succeeded, is in progress, or has failed.
    AzureClient
    An instance of this class defines a ServiceClient that handles polling and retrying for long running operations when accessing Azure resources.
    AzureEnvironment
    An instance of this class describes an environment in Azure.
    AzureResponse<T>
    A standard service response including request ID.
    AzureServiceClient
    ServiceClient is the abstraction for accessing REST operations and their payload data types.
    AzureServiceResponseBuilder<T,E extends RestException>
    The builder for building a ServiceResponse.
    CloudError
    An instance of this class provides additional information about an http error response.
    CustomHeaderInterceptor
    An instance of this class enables adding custom headers in client requests when added to the OkHttpClient interceptors.
    DAGNode<T>
    The type representing node in a DAGraph.
    DAGraph<T,U extends DAGNode<T>>
    Type representing a DAG (directed acyclic graph).
    Graph<T,U extends Node<T>>
    Type representing a directed graph data structure.
    ListOperationCallback<E>
    The callback used for client side asynchronous list operations.
    Node<T>
    Type represents a node in a Graph.
    PagedList<E>
    Defines a list response from a paging operation.
    PollingState<T>
    An instance of this class defines the state of a long running operation.
    RequestIdHeaderInterceptor
    An instance of this class puts an UUID in the request header.
    Resource
    The Resource model.
    ResourceGetExponentialBackoffRetryStrategy
    A retry strategy with backoff parameters for calculating the exponential delay between retries for 404s from GET calls.
    RestClient

    RestClient.Builder
    The builder class for building a REST client.
    SubResource
    The SubResource model.
    TaskGroupBase<T,U extends TaskItem<T>>
